{"tid":1392493,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"試著說”你已失去正當執法權利，立即解除武裝接受拘捕”，不要說”黑警，我攞你命”","createTime":"2019-07-31T18:19:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T19:27:57.000Z","uid":137721,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bed31ea6e1246c2d0e4581e1c914fa86c288e45d","tid":1392493,"uid":137721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:19:01.000Z","msg":"葵青一役話俾我地知<br />\n<strong>要贏，就只有<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">主動出擊</span></strong></strong><br />\n<br />\n為此我地需要一個正當性，就係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">作出宣告</span></strong><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">你已失去市民認受性/你並非正當執行職務，請立即解除武裝，否則將會行使101拘捕令\n</code></pre><br />\n但各位手足記住，要令呢個宣告有效而不招話柄<br />\n我地要做既係<strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">拘捕同卸甲</span></strong></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">而唔係盲目發洩仇恨</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好再傻豬豬等啲popo齊裝，同畜龍硬碰硬<br />\n係膠著既時候作出宣告，會有意思不到既效果"},{"pid":"c8d6c9037d394c42385c2508947eabb2648d6b3b","tid":1392493,"uid":137721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:22:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb7e6c75cb545c992769f6b45b387ec0471661b9","tid":1392493,"uid":137721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:23:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08a5ce9cd3add0b5197ccff7946e0846c96e3956","tid":1392493,"uid":276382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:23:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"edf15d93f9fe6040b5bd97bf1e9b59d19db17b1c","tid":1392493,"uid":137721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:23:58.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人&nbsp;<br />\n#我會參與罷工罷市罷課<br />\n<br />\n8月2日 公務員罷工集會<br />\n8月5日 一齊罷工 7區集會"},{"pid":"13f4ea53cbbaf371c697415c18f73cdc55566c53","tid":1392493,"uid":289683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited